Anglo Platinum May Boost Wage Offer After Workers Cut Demands, Union Says

-- B y   C a r l i   L o u r e n s
-- 
2011-07-28T10:32:54Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-28/anglo-platinum-may-boost-wage-offer-after-workers-cut-demands-union-says.html
Anglo American Platinum Ltd. workers
dropped their pay-increase demand to 15 percent from 20 percent,
Oupa Komane, a  National Union of Mineworkers  spokesman in  South
Africa , said by phone.  The company will probably revise its 4.6 percent offer
today, he said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Carli Lourens at 
 clourens@bloomberg.net  